flowchart TD
    BuildArtifact[Receive build artifact] --> GenerateVersion[Generate version label SHA plus semver]
    GenerateVersion --> Upload[Upload artifact to registry]
    Upload --> WriteMetadata[Write build metadata to artifact]
    WriteMetadata --> ComputeDigest[Compute SHA-256 digest]
    ComputeDigest --> StoreInventory[Record artifact in release inventory]
    StoreInventory --> PromoteGate{Promoted to production?}
    PromoteGate -->|Yes| RetainLong[Apply long-term retention policy]
    PromoteGate -->|No| RetainShort[Apply short-term retention policy]
    RetainLong --> Done[Artifact available for deployment]
    RetainShort --> GCCheck{Retention window expired?}
    GCCheck -->|No| Done
    GCCheck -->|Yes| GarbageCollect[Delete stale artifact]
